msgid "An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings and destroy blocks around it. TNT has an explosion radius of @1. With a small chance, blocks may drop as an item (as if being mined) rather than being destroyed. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals."
msgstr ""
"一种爆炸装置。当其爆炸时，会对生物造成伤害并破坏周围的方块。TNT的爆炸半径为@1"
"。有较小的几率，方块可能会作为物品掉落（就好像是被开采过一样），而不是直接被"
"摧毁。TNT可以通过工具、爆炸、火焰、岩浆以及红石信号来引爆。"

msgid "An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings. TNT has an explosion radius of @1. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals."
msgstr "一种爆炸装置。当其爆炸时，会对生物造成伤害。TNT的爆炸半径为@1。TNT可以通过工"
"具、爆炸、火焰、岩浆以及红石信号来引爆。"

msgid "TNT"
msgstr "TNT（炸药）"

msgid "Ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava, redstone power"
msgstr "可由工具、爆炸、火焰、岩浆、红石能量来引燃"

msgid "Explosion radius: @1"
msgstr "爆炸半径：@1"

msgid "Place the TNT and ignite it with one of the methods above. Quickly get in safe distance. The TNT will start to be affected by gravity and explodes in 4 seconds."
msgstr "放置好TNT，然后用上述方法之一将其引燃。迅速撤离到安全距离之外。TNT将开始受重"
"力影响，并在4秒后爆炸。"
